outputs.output_descr: the project aims at developing the capacity of local NGOSs in generating environmental and livelihood benefits through implementing local solutions for global environmental problems such as climate change. it  focuses on implementing creative solutions that also solve environmental and livelihood problem for  the poor in marginalized area.

project_descr: the project aims at developing the capacities of local NGos in generating environmental and livelihood benefits for local communities through implementing initiatives that addressed the five global environmental problems
